articles.author: Jeffrey Clark
articles.title: CNN guest calls out network for saying Israelis rescued from Hamas was 'hostage release' - Fox News
articles.description: Eurasia Group president Ian Bremmer said that he was "disappointed to see" CNN's misleading news chyron calling an Israeli operation to rescue hostages a "release."
